426
00:40:49,917 --> 00:40:52,125
Often in my dreams at night,

427
00:40:52,625 --> 00:40:55,583
I live in those glorious times.

428
00:40:56,292 --> 00:40:58,667
I too am at the feast

429
00:41:00,292 --> 00:41:02,417
