504
00:46:44,625 --> 00:46:45,666
I was there.

505
00:46:45,792 --> 00:46:46,625
Where?

506
00:46:46,958 --> 00:46:48,124
At the banquet.

507
00:46:50,500 --> 00:46:51,583
Which banquet?

508
00:46:54,542 --> 00:46:56,958
