539
00:49:14,042 --> 00:49:15,333
Cat skin?

540
00:49:36,667 --> 00:49:39,958
Master Kukai, thank you.

541
00:49:40,500 --> 00:49:41,833
Scribe Bai.

542
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:11,958
How dare they play banned music.

543
