Yunqiao!

548
00:51:02,750 --> 00:51:05,500
You brought on this disaster!

549
00:51:06,875 --> 00:51:08,500
It's your fault!

550
00:51:08,708 --> 00:51:09,958
Stop it!

551
00:51:11,375 --> 00:51:12,643
I want you dead!

552
00:51:12,667 --> 00:51:14,417
Kukai! Save Chunqin!

